### Health check - Liveness
GET http://localhost:8080/livez

### Health check - Readiness
GET http://localhost:8080/readyz

### List all available tools
GET http://localhost:8080/mcp/tools

### ===== LLM GENERATE =====

### Simple text generation with OpenAI
POST http://localhost:8080/mcp/invoke
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tool": "llm_generate",
  "arguments": {
    "provider": "openai",
    "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
    "messages": [
      {"role": "user", "content": "What is the capital of France?"}
    ]
  }
}

### Text generation with Anthropic
POST http://localhost:8080/mcp/invoke
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tool": "llm_generate",
  "arguments": {
    "provider": "anthropic",
    "model": "claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022",
    "messages": [
      {"role": "user", "content": "Explain quantum computing in one paragraph"}
    ],
    "opts": {
      "temperature": 0.3,
      "max_tokens": 150
    }
  }
}

### Text generation with Gemini
POST http://localhost:8080/mcp/invoke
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tool": "llm_generate",
  "arguments": {
    "provider": "gemini",
    "model": "gemini-1.5-flash",
    "messages": [
      {"role": "user", "content": "What are the benefits of renewable energy?"}
    ]
  }
}

### Vision example with multimodal content (Anthropic)
# Replace with actual base64 image data
POST http://localhost:8080/mcp/invoke
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tool": "llm_generate",
  "arguments": {
    "provider": "anthropic",
    "model": "claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022",
    "modality": "vision",
    "messages": [
      {
        "role": "user",
        "content": [
          {"type": "text", "data": "What is in this image?"},
          {"type": "image", "data": "https://example.com/image.jpg"}
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}

### Streaming text generation
POST http://localhost:8080/mcp/invoke?stream=true
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tool": "llm_generate",
  "arguments": {
    "provider": "openai",
    "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
    "messages": [
      {"role": "user", "content": "Write a short poem about programming"}
    ]
  }
}

### ===== COMPARE MODELS =====

### Compare OpenAI and Anthropic
POST http://localhost:8080/mcp/invoke
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tool": "compare_models",
  "arguments": {
    "prompt": "Explain machine learning in simple terms",
    "a": {
      "provider": "openai",
      "model": "gpt-4o-mini"
    },
    "b": {
      "provider": "anthropic",
      "model": "claude-3-haiku-20240307"
    },
    "opts": {
      "temperature": 0.5,
      "max_tokens": 200
    }
  }
}

### Compare Gemini and Grok
POST http://localhost:8080/mcp/invoke
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tool": "compare_models",
  "arguments": {
    "prompt": "What is the future of AI?",
    "a": {
      "provider": "gemini",
      "model": "gemini-1.5-flash"
    },
    "b": {
      "provider": "grok",
      "model": "grok-beta"
    }
  }
}

### ===== PLAN EXECUTE =====

### Simple task decomposition
POST http://localhost:8080/mcp/invoke
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tool": "plan_execute",
  "arguments": {
    "goal": "Research renewable energy trends and create a summary",
    "constraints": ["Keep responses concise", "Focus on 2024 developments"],
    "tools_allowed": ["llm_generate"],
    "decomposer": {
      "provider": "anthropic",
      "model": "claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022"
    },
    "opts": {
      "max_depth": 3
    }
  }
}

### Complex planning task
POST http://localhost:8080/mcp/invoke
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tool": "plan_execute",
  "arguments": {
    "goal": "Analyze the impact of AI on healthcare and education",
    "constraints": [
      "Include statistics where possible",
      "Consider ethical implications",
      "Maximum 100 tokens per step"
    ],
    "tools_allowed": ["llm_generate", "search"],
    "decomposer": {
      "provider": "openai",
      "model": "gpt-4o-mini"
    },
    "opts": {
      "max_depth": 5
    }
  }
}

### Simple goal with minimal steps
POST http://localhost:8080/mcp/invoke
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tool": "plan_execute",
  "arguments": {
    "goal": "Explain blockchain technology",
    "decomposer": {
      "provider": "gemini",
      "model": "gemini-1.5-flash"
    }
  }
}
